<div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="sm:mx-auto sm:w-full sm:max-w-2xl" data-testid="kickoff-booked">
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-3">📅</div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Kickoff booked. We'll be in touch.</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-lg text-gray-600">
        Your specialist will email you within one business day to confirm a time and walk through pricing.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow space-y-3">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">What you told us</h3>
      <% if @scheduling_form.timezone.present? %>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-700"><span class="font-medium">Time zone:</span> <%= @scheduling_form.timezone %></div>
      <% end %>
      <% if @scheduling_form.any_days? %>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-700"><span class="font-medium">Days that work:</span> <%= @scheduling_form.day_labels %></div>
      <% end %>
      <% if @scheduling_form.any_time_blocks? %>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-700"><span class="font-medium">Times that work:</span> <%= @scheduling_form.time_block_labels %></div>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 text-center text-sm text-gray-600">
      <p>While you wait, you can <%= link_to "head to your dashboard", dashboard_path, class: "text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 font-medium" %>. There's nothing for you to do here — we'll handle the installation after the call.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
